{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "凡出言談，則必可而不先立儀而言。", "text_normalized": "凡出言談，則必可而不先立儀而言。", "canonical_ref": "29.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "若不先立儀而言，譬之猶運鈞之上而立朝夕焉也，我以為雖有朝夕之辯，必將終未可得而從定也。", "text_normalized": "若不先立儀而言，譬之猶運鈞之上而立朝夕焉也，我以為雖有朝夕之辯，必將終未可得而從定也。", "canonical_ref": "29.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "是故言有三法。", "text_normalized": "是故言有三法。", "canonical_ref": "29.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "何謂三法？", "text_normalized": "何謂三法？", "canonical_ref": "29.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "有考之者，有原之者，有用之者。", "text_normalized": "有考之者，有原之者，有用之者。", "canonical_ref": "29.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "惡乎考之？", "text_normalized": "惡乎考之？", "canonical_ref": "29.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "考先聖大王之事。", "text_normalized": "考先聖大王之事。", "canonical_ref": "29.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "惡乎原之？", "text_normalized": "惡乎原之？", "canonical_ref": "29.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "察眾之耳目之請。", "text_normalized": "察眾之耳目之請。", "canonical_ref": "29.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "惡乎用之？", "text_normalized": "惡乎用之？", "canonical_ref": "29.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "發而為政乎國，察萬民而觀之。", "text_normalized": "發而為政乎國，察萬民而觀之。", "canonical_ref": "29.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "此謂三法也。", "text_normalized": "此謂三法也。", "canonical_ref": "29.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "故昔者三代聖王禹、湯、文、武方為政乎天下之時，曰：", "text_normalized": "故昔者三代聖王禹、湯、文、武方為政乎天下之時，曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "「必務舉孝子而勸之事親，尊賢良之人而教之為善。", "text_normalized": "「必務舉孝子而勸之事親，尊賢良之人而教之為善。", "canonical_ref": "29.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "」是故出政施教，賞善罰暴。", "text_normalized": "」是故出政施教，賞善罰暴。", "canonical_ref": "29.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "且以為若此，則天下之亂也，將屬可得而治也；", "text_normalized": "且以為若此，則天下之亂也，將屬可得而治也；", "canonical_ref": "29.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "社稷之危也，將屬可得而定也。", "text_normalized": "社稷之危也，將屬可得而定也。", "canonical_ref": "29.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "若以為不然，昔桀之所亂，湯治之。", "text_normalized": "若以為不然，昔桀之所亂，湯治之。", "canonical_ref": "29.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "紂之所亂，武王治之。", "text_normalized": "紂之所亂，武王治之。", "canonical_ref": "29.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "當此之時，世不渝而民不易，上變政而民改俗。", "text_normalized": "當此之時，世不渝而民不易，上變政而民改俗。", "canonical_ref": "29.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "存乎桀、紂而天下亂，存乎湯、武而天下治。", "text_normalized": "存乎桀、紂而天下亂，存乎湯、武而天下治。", "canonical_ref": "29.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "天下之治也，湯、武之力也。", "text_normalized": "天下之治也，湯、武之力也。", "canonical_ref": "29.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "天下之亂也，桀、紂之罪也。", "text_normalized": "天下之亂也，桀、紂之罪也。", "canonical_ref": "29.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "若以此觀之，夫安危治亂，存乎上之為政也，則夫豈可謂有命哉！", "text_normalized": "若以此觀之，夫安危治亂，存乎上之為政也，則夫豈可謂有命哉！", "canonical_ref": "29.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "故昔者禹、湯、文、武方為政乎天下之時，曰：", "text_normalized": "故昔者禹、湯、文、武方為政乎天下之時，曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "「必使饑者得食，寒者得衣，勞者得息，亂者得治。", "text_normalized": "「必使饑者得食，寒者得衣，勞者得息，亂者得治。", "canonical_ref": "29.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "」遂得光譽令問於天下。", "text_normalized": "」遂得光譽令問於天下。", "canonical_ref": "29.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "夫豈可以為命哉？", "text_normalized": "夫豈可以為命哉？", "canonical_ref": "29.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "故以為其力也。", "text_normalized": "故以為其力也。", "canonical_ref": "29.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "今賢良之人，尊賢而好功道術，故上得其王公大人之賞，下得其萬民之譽，遂得光譽令問於天下。", "text_normalized": "今賢良之人，尊賢而好功道術，故上得其王公大人之賞，下得其萬民之譽，遂得光譽令問於天下。", "canonical_ref": "29.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "亦豈以為其命哉？", "text_normalized": "亦豈以為其命哉？", "canonical_ref": "29.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "又以為力也。", "text_normalized": "又以為力也。", "canonical_ref": "29.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "然今夫有命者，不識昔也三代之聖善人與？", "text_normalized": "然今夫有命者，不識昔也三代之聖善人與？", "canonical_ref": "29.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "意亡昔三代之暴不肖人與？", "text_normalized": "意亡昔三代之暴不肖人與？", "canonical_ref": "29.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "若以說觀之，則必非昔三代聖善人也，必暴不肖人也。", "text_normalized": "若以說觀之，則必非昔三代聖善人也，必暴不肖人也。", "canonical_ref": "29.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "然今以命為有者，昔三代暴王桀、紂、幽、厲，貴為天子，富有天下，於此乎不而矯其耳目之欲，而從其心意之辟，外之馳騁田獵畢弋，內湛於酒樂，而不顧其國家百姓之政。", "text_normalized": "然今以命為有者，昔三代暴王桀、紂、幽、厲，貴為天子，富有天下，於此乎不而矯其耳目之欲，而從其心意之辟，外之馳騁田獵畢弋，內湛於酒樂，而不顧其國家百姓之政。", "canonical_ref": "29.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "繁為無用，暴逆百姓，遂失其宗廟。", "text_normalized": "繁為無用，暴逆百姓，遂失其宗廟。", "canonical_ref": "29.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "其言不曰：", "text_normalized": "其言不曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "吾罷不肖，吾聽治不強。", "text_normalized": "吾罷不肖，吾聽治不強。", "canonical_ref": "29.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "必曰：", "text_normalized": "必曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "吾命固將失之。", "text_normalized": "吾命固將失之。", "canonical_ref": "29.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "雖昔也三代罷不肖之民，亦猶此也。", "text_normalized": "雖昔也三代罷不肖之民，亦猶此也。", "canonical_ref": "29.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "不能善事親戚、君長，甚惡恭儉而好簡易，貪飲食而惰從事，衣食之財不足，是以身有陷乎饑寒凍餒之憂。", "text_normalized": "不能善事親戚、君長，甚惡恭儉而好簡易，貪飲食而惰從事，衣食之財不足，是以身有陷乎饑寒凍餒之憂。", "canonical_ref": "29.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "其言不曰：", "text_normalized": "其言不曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "吾罷不肖，吾從事不強。", "text_normalized": "吾罷不肖，吾從事不強。", "canonical_ref": "29.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "又曰：", "text_normalized": "又曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "吾命固將窮。", "text_normalized": "吾命固將窮。", "canonical_ref": "29.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "昔三代偽民，亦猶此也。", "text_normalized": "昔三代偽民，亦猶此也。", "canonical_ref": "29.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "昔者暴王作之，窮人術之，此皆疑眾遲樸。", "text_normalized": "昔者暴王作之，窮人術之，此皆疑眾遲樸。", "canonical_ref": "29.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "先聖王之患之也，固在前矣。", "text_normalized": "先聖王之患之也，固在前矣。", "canonical_ref": "29.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "是以書之竹帛，鏤之金石，琢之盤盂，傳遺後世子孫。", "text_normalized": "是以書之竹帛，鏤之金石，琢之盤盂，傳遺後世子孫。", "canonical_ref": "29.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "何書焉存？", "text_normalized": "何書焉存？", "canonical_ref": "29.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "禹之《總德》有之，曰：", "text_normalized": "禹之《總德》有之，曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "「允不著，惟天民不而葆。", "text_normalized": "「允不著，惟天民不而葆。", "canonical_ref": "29.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "既防凶心，天加之咎。", "text_normalized": "既防凶心，天加之咎。", "canonical_ref": "29.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "不慎厥德，天命焉葆？", "text_normalized": "不慎厥德，天命焉葆？", "canonical_ref": "29.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "」《仲虺之告》曰：", "text_normalized": "」《仲虺之告》曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "「我聞有夏人矯天命，於下，帝式是增，用爽厥師。", "text_normalized": "「我聞有夏人矯天命，於下，帝式是增，用爽厥師。", "canonical_ref": "29.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "」彼用無為有，故謂矯。", "text_normalized": "」彼用無為有，故謂矯。", "canonical_ref": "29.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "若有而謂有，夫豈謂矯哉！", "text_normalized": "若有而謂有，夫豈謂矯哉！", "canonical_ref": "29.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "昔者，桀執有命而行，湯為《仲虺之告》以非之。", "text_normalized": "昔者，桀執有命而行，湯為《仲虺之告》以非之。", "canonical_ref": "29.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "《太誓》之言也，於《去發》曰：", "text_normalized": "《太誓》之言也，於《去發》曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "「惡乎君子！", "text_normalized": "「惡乎君子！", "canonical_ref": "29.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "天有顯德，其行甚章。", "text_normalized": "天有顯德，其行甚章。", "canonical_ref": "29.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "為鑒不遠，在彼殷王。", "text_normalized": "為鑒不遠，在彼殷王。", "canonical_ref": "29.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "謂人有命，謂敬不可行，謂祭無益，謂暴無傷。", "text_normalized": "謂人有命，謂敬不可行，謂祭無益，謂暴無傷。", "canonical_ref": "29.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "上帝不常，九有以亡。", "text_normalized": "上帝不常，九有以亡。", "canonical_ref": "29.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "上帝不順，祝降其喪。", "text_normalized": "上帝不順，祝降其喪。", "canonical_ref": "29.71", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 72, "text_original": "惟我有周，受之大帝。", "text_normalized": "惟我有周，受之大帝。", "canonical_ref": "29.72", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 73, "text_original": "」昔紂執有命而行，武王為《太誓》、《去發》以非之。", "text_normalized": "」昔紂執有命而行，武王為《太誓》、《去發》以非之。", "canonical_ref": "29.73", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0074", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 74, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.74", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 75, "text_original": "子胡不尚考之乎商、周、虞、夏之記？", "text_normalized": "子胡不尚考之乎商、周、虞、夏之記？", "canonical_ref": "29.75", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 76, "text_original": "從十簡之篇以尚皆無之，將何若者也？", "text_normalized": "從十簡之篇以尚皆無之，將何若者也？", "canonical_ref": "29.76", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 77, "text_original": "是故子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.77", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 78, "text_original": "今天下之君子之為文學、出言談也，非將勤勞其惟舌，而利其唇呡也，中實將欲其國家邑里萬民刑政者也。", "text_normalized": "今天下之君子之為文學、出言談也，非將勤勞其惟舌，而利其唇呡也，中實將欲其國家邑里萬民刑政者也。", "canonical_ref": "29.78", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0079", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 79, "text_original": "今也王公大人之所以蚤朝晏退，聽獄治政，終朝均分而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "text_normalized": "今也王公大人之所以蚤朝晏退，聽獄治政，終朝均分而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "29.79", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0080", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 80, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.80", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0081", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 81, "text_original": "彼以為強必治，不強必亂，強必寧，不強必危，故不敢怠倦。", "text_normalized": "彼以為強必治，不強必亂，強必寧，不強必危，故不敢怠倦。", "canonical_ref": "29.81", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0082", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 82, "text_original": "今也卿大夫之所以竭股肱之力，殫其思慮之知，內治官府，外斂關市、山林、澤梁之利，以實官府而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "text_normalized": "今也卿大夫之所以竭股肱之力，殫其思慮之知，內治官府，外斂關市、山林、澤梁之利，以實官府而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "29.82", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0083", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 83, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.83", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0084", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 84, "text_original": "彼以為強必貴，不強必賤。", "text_normalized": "彼以為強必貴，不強必賤。", "canonical_ref": "29.84", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0085", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 85, "text_original": "強必榮，不強必辱，故不敢怠倦。", "text_normalized": "強必榮，不強必辱，故不敢怠倦。", "canonical_ref": "29.85", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0086", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 86, "text_original": "今也農夫之所以蚤出暮入，強乎耕稼樹蓺，多聚叔粟而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "text_normalized": "今也農夫之所以蚤出暮入，強乎耕稼樹蓺，多聚叔粟而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "29.86", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0087", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 87, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.87", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0088", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 88, "text_original": "彼以為強必富，不強必貧，強必飽，不強必饑，故不敢怠倦。", "text_normalized": "彼以為強必富，不強必貧，強必飽，不強必饑，故不敢怠倦。", "canonical_ref": "29.88", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0089", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 89, "text_original": "今也婦人之所以夙興夜寐，強乎紡績織紝，多治麻絲葛緒，捆布縿而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "text_normalized": "今也婦人之所以夙興夜寐，強乎紡績織紝，多治麻絲葛緒，捆布縿而不敢怠倦者，何也？", "canonical_ref": "29.89", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0090", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 90, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.90", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0091", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 91, "text_original": "彼以為強必富，不強必貧，強必暖，不強必寒，故不敢怠倦。", "text_normalized": "彼以為強必富，不強必貧，強必暖，不強必寒，故不敢怠倦。", "canonical_ref": "29.91", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0092", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 92, "text_original": "今雖毋在乎王公大人，蕢若信有命而致行之，則必怠乎聽獄治政矣，卿人夫必怠乎治官府矣，農夫必怠乎耕稼樹蓺矣，婦人必怠乎紡績織紝矣。", "text_normalized": "今雖毋在乎王公大人，蕢若信有命而致行之，則必怠乎聽獄治政矣，卿人夫必怠乎治官府矣，農夫必怠乎耕稼樹蓺矣，婦人必怠乎紡績織紝矣。", "canonical_ref": "29.92", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0093", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 93, "text_original": "王公大人怠乎聽獄治政，卿大夫怠乎治官府，則我以為天下必亂矣。", "text_normalized": "王公大人怠乎聽獄治政，卿大夫怠乎治官府，則我以為天下必亂矣。", "canonical_ref": "29.93", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0094", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 94, "text_original": "農夫怠乎耕稼樹蓺，婦人怠乎紡績織紝，則我以為天下衣食之財將必不足矣。", "text_normalized": "農夫怠乎耕稼樹蓺，婦人怠乎紡績織紝，則我以為天下衣食之財將必不足矣。", "canonical_ref": "29.94", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0095", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 95, "text_original": "若以為政乎天下，上以事天鬼，天鬼不使；", "text_normalized": "若以為政乎天下，上以事天鬼，天鬼不使；", "canonical_ref": "29.95", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0096", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 96, "text_original": "下以持養百姓，百姓不利，必離散不可得用也。", "text_normalized": "下以持養百姓，百姓不利，必離散不可得用也。", "canonical_ref": "29.96", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0097", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 97, "text_original": "是以入守則不固，出誅則不勝。", "text_normalized": "是以入守則不固，出誅則不勝。", "canonical_ref": "29.97", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0098", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 98, "text_original": "故雖昔者三代暴王桀、紂、幽、厲之所以共抎其國家、傾覆其社稷者，此也。", "text_normalized": "故雖昔者三代暴王桀、紂、幽、厲之所以共抎其國家、傾覆其社稷者，此也。", "canonical_ref": "29.98", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0099", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 99, "text_original": "是故子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "是故子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.99", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0100", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 100, "text_original": "今天下之士君子，中實將欲求興天下之利，除天下之害，當若執有命者之言，不可不強非也。", "text_normalized": "今天下之士君子，中實將欲求興天下之利，除天下之害，當若執有命者之言，不可不強非也。", "canonical_ref": "29.100", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0101", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 101, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "29.101", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0102", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 102, "text_original": "命者，暴王所作，窮人所術，非仁者之言也。", "text_normalized": "命者，暴王所作，窮人所術，非仁者之言也。", "canonical_ref": "29.102", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0103", "section_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii", "source_id": "mozi-029-anti-fatalism-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 103, "text_original": "今之為仁義者，將不可不察而強非者此也。", "text_normalized": "今之為仁義者，將不可不察而強非者此也。", "canonical_ref": "29.103", "notes": ""}
